---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const jsonLd = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebPage",
  "name": "Disclosure",
  "description": "TendersMW's disclosure explaining how we operate, our data sources, and our relationship with procurement entities.",
  "url": "https://tendersmw.com/disclosure/",
  "datePublished": "2026-03-26",
  "dateModified": "2026-03-26"
};
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Disclosure | How TendersMW Operates"
  description="TendersMW's full disclosure. Learn how we source tender data, how we may earn revenue in the future, and our commitment to accurate procurement information."
  jsonLd={jsonLd}
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-primary uppercase tracking-wider mb-6">Disclosure</span>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text mb-2">Disclosure</h1>
    <p class="text-muted mb-8">Transparency is one of our core values. Here's exactly how TendersMW operates and how we source procurement data.</p>

    <div class="space-y-8">

      <div class="glass-card p-6 border border-primary/20">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-4">Important Notice</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
          TendersMW is owned and operated by Cosmic Phoenix LLC. We aggregate publicly available procurement notices from government and international development sources. <strong class="text-text">We are not affiliated with, endorsed by, or officially connected to the Public Procurement and Disposal of Assets Authority (PPDA) or any government ministry.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
          All tender information displayed on this site is sourced from publicly available government portals and international procurement databases. We present this information as a convenience to businesses seeking procurement opportunities in Malawi.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-4">How We Source Data</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
          TendersMW aggregates procurement notices from the following public sources:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-muted">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary shrink-0">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-text">PPDA (ppda.mw)</strong> -- The Public Procurement and Disposal of Assets Authority's official tender portal</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary shrink-0">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-text">MANEPS (maneps.mw)</strong> -- Malawi National E-Procurement System, the government's new digital procurement platform</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary shrink-0">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-text">World Bank Procurement</strong> -- International development project tenders in Malawi</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary shrink-0">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-text">African Development Bank (AfDB)</strong> -- Regional development procurement</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary shrink-0">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-text">EU TED (Tenders Electronic Daily)</strong> -- European-funded development tenders</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary shrink-0">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-text">UNGM (United Nations Global Marketplace)</strong> -- UN agency procurement in Malawi</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-4">How We May Earn Revenue</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
          TendersMW is currently a free service. In the future, we may earn revenue through:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-muted">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary shrink-0">&#9679;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-text">Premium alerts:</strong> Paid email or SMS notifications for new tenders matching specific criteria</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary shrink-0">&#9679;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-text">Tender preparation consulting:</strong> Assistance with bid document preparation and compliance</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary shrink-0">&#9679;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-text">Sponsored listings:</strong> Procurement-related service providers (legal, financial, logistics) may pay for visibility, always clearly labeled as "Sponsored"</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mt-4">
          Revenue arrangements will never influence which tenders we display, how we categorize them, or the accuracy of the information presented. All tender data is sourced directly from official portals.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-4">What This Means for You</h2>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-muted">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-400 shrink-0">&#10003;</span>
            <p><strong class="text-text">Free access to tender information.</strong> All publicly sourced tender data is available at no cost.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-400 shrink-0">&#10003;</span>
            <p><strong class="text-text">No hidden fees.</strong> You will never be charged without explicitly opting into a paid service.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-400 shrink-0">&#10003;</span>
            <p><strong class="text-text">Always verify with the source.</strong> We encourage all bidders to verify tender details directly with the procuring entity or on the official source portal before submitting bids.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-4">Questions About Our Disclosure</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
          If you have any questions about how we operate, our data sources, or our business model, please contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@tendersmw.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact@tendersmw.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-xs text-muted text-center">
        Last updated: March 26, 2026 | TendersMW is a property of Cosmic Phoenix LLC.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
